org.sql: SELECT journals.id AS event_id, journals.created_at AS event_datetime, journals.user_id AS event_author, journals.notes AS event_description, journals.version AS version, journals.journable_id AS journable_id, wikis.project_id AS project_id, wiki_pages.title AS wiki_title, wiki_pages.slug AS wiki_slug FROM journals INNER JOIN wiki_content_journals ON journals.data_id = wiki_content_journals.id AND journals.data_type = 'Journal::WikiContentJournal' INNER JOIN wiki_pages ON wiki_content_journals.page_id = wiki_pages.id INNER JOIN wikis ON wiki_pages.wiki_id = wikis.id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = wikis.project_id WHERE journals.journable_type = 'WikiContent' AND journals.user_id = 653 AND projects.id IN (SELECT enabled_modules.project_id FROM enabled_modules WHERE name = 'activity') AND projects.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT projects.id FROM projects LEFT OUTER JOIN members ON projects.id = members.project_id AND members.user_id = 670 AND projects.active = True INNER JOIN enabled_modules ON projects.id = enabled_modules.project_id AND enabled_modules.name IN ('wiki') AND projects.active = True INNER JOIN role_permissions ON role_permissions.permission IN ('view_wiki_edits') INNER JOIN roles AS permission_roles ON permission_roles.id = role_permissions.role_id LEFT OUTER JOIN member_roles ON members.id = member_roles.member_id LEFT OUTER JOIN roles AS assigned_roles ON assigned_roles.id = permission_roles.id AND projects.active = True AND (assigned_roles.id = member_roles.role_id OR projects.public = True AND assigned_roles.builtin = 1 AND member_roles.id IS NULL) WHERE assigned_roles.id IS NOT NULL) ORDER BY journals.id DESC LIMIT 10
